{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回「山巅晨雾浓如烟」中，展梦白在山巅遭遇黑衣女子萧三夫人与其仆从方巨木的冲突。萧三夫人对方巨木施以耳光，展梦白因怜悯而出手相助，却反遭萧三夫人掌掴。展梦白愤怒离去，方巨木阻拦并与其交手。展梦白虽功力不及方巨木，但刚猛拳法与愤怒加持使其略占上风。关键时刻，萧三夫人指点展梦白破敌之招，却因展梦白迟疑而未能成功，萧三夫人亲自出手击退方巨木。随后方巨木认出展梦白是展化雨之子，态度转为恭敬，叩首告退。萧三夫人因旧疾发作昏厥，展梦白悉心照料。苏浅雪现身救下被方巨木围攻的展梦白，原来苏浅雪正是萧三夫人所提之人。萧三夫人带回一名黑衣大汉与金色牧笛，与苏浅雪形成对峙。全章展现展梦白的善良与刚烈，以及萧三夫人、苏浅雪之间复杂的过往纠葛。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们怎么知道我到了杭州？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ju_mu",
      "speaker_name": "方巨木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只是小人们的猜想……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还笑！笑什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小人不敢，小人只是奉主公之命，前来迎接夫人，夫人身体不好，若是劳顿过度……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "主公",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ju_mu",
      "speaker_name": "方巨木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人纵是与主公误会，回到谷中，主公自会向夫人解说，夫人又何苦当着一个外人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣女子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧三夫人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只听",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧夫人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧三夫人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "口中却沉声道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧三夫人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁的家事？什么家事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "萧三夫人",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ju_mu",
      "speaker_name": "方巨木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回去！",
