      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你回去……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ju_mu",
      "speaker_name": "方巨木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不回去了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ju_mu",
      "speaker_name": "方巨木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_ju_mu",
      "speaker_name": "方巨木",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小人……听……听得很清楚，但夫人你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听清楚了，还不快走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她与我素昧平生，为何对我的态度竟是如此奇怪……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "夫人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快……快……我怀里的黑盒子……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苍天，感激你终于还是让我多活些日子……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不知道有多久了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你一直守着我？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也不知道为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好孩子！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你认不认得一个叫苏浅雪的女人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些年来，爹爹提起的只有我死去的母亲……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "见谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_san_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "萧三夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苏浅雪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_meng_bai",
      "speaker_name": "展梦白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方巨木！",
      "tone": "陈述",
